Q. Why main method is static?
A. Java main() method is always static, so that compiler can call it without the creation of an object
or before the creation of an object of the class.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Q. Which class is the superclass of all classes in java?
A. Class Object is the root of the class hierarchy. Every class has Object as a superclass.

